    {
        "url": "/quotes/ron_chernow_290832",
        "quote": "In the 1920s, Wall Street was a world that was really dominated by professional speculators and stock pools. These people had a monopoly over information.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Ron Chernow",
            "url": "/quotes/ron_chernow_290832"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Over",
                "url": "/topics/over"
            },
            {
                "name": "1920s",
                "url": "/topics/1920s"
            },
            {
                "name": "Pools",
                "url": "/topics/pools"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/ron_chernow_290833",
        "quote": "The securities laws of the 1930s were so important because it forced companies to file registration statements and issue prospectuses, and it remedied the imbalance of information.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Ron Chernow",
            "url": "/quotes/ron_chernow_290833"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "1930s",
                "url": "/topics/1930s"
            },
            {
                "name": "Laws",
                "url": "/topics/laws"
            },
            {
                "name": "Imbalance",
                "url": "/topics/imbalance"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/ron_chernow_290835",
        "quote": "In the 1920s you could buy stocks on margin. You could put 10 percent down and borrow the rest against your stocks.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Ron Chernow",
            "url": "/quotes/ron_chernow_290835"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Rest",
                "url": "/topics/rest"
            },
            {
                "name": "1920s",
                "url": "/topics/1920s"
            },
            {
                "name": "Margin",
                "url": "/topics/margin"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/ron_chernow_290838",
        "quote": "When news of the crash came, probably a lot of people in small towns and farms across America felt a sense of grim satisfaction that the sinners had finally been punished for their wicked ways.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Ron Chernow",
            "url": "/quotes/ron_chernow_290838"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Small",
                "url": "/topics/small"
