            {
                "name": "Going",
                "url": "/topics/going"
            },
            {
                "name": "Over",
                "url": "/topics/over"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/ron_chernow_290857",
        "quote": "I'm dubious about having Social Security put into the stock market. I think that we have gotten very far away from the idea that there's something sacrosanct about retirement investments.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Ron Chernow",
            "url": "/quotes/ron_chernow_290857"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Away",
                "url": "/topics/away"
            },
            {
                "name": "I Think",
                "url": "/topics/i_think"
            },
            {
                "name": "Very",
                "url": "/topics/very"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/ron_chernow_290858",
        "quote": "We really haven't had very much experience with people funding their retirement out of the stock market, and we don't know, frankly, how it would work under every scenario.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Ron Chernow",
            "url": "/quotes/ron_chernow_290858"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Work",
                "url": "/topics/work"
            },
            {
                "name": "Very",
                "url": "/topics/very"
            },
            {
                "name": "Funding",
                "url": "/topics/funding"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/ron_chernow_290863",
        "quote": "The mutual fund industry and small investors are very relentless and very unforgiving if people don't perform.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Ron Chernow",
            "url": "/quotes/ron_chernow_290863"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Small",
                "url": "/topics/small"
            },
            {
                "name": "Very",
                "url": "/topics/very"
            },
            {
                "name": "Perform",
                "url": "/topics/perform"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/ron_chernow_290864",
        "quote": "Mutual fund managers are trapped in this rather deadly vicious circle: the more successful they are, the more money flows into their mutual fund. Then, it is more difficult for them to beat the market averages or even to match their own past performance.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Ron Chernow",
            "url": "/quotes/ron_chernow_290864"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Own",
                "url": "/topics/own"
            },
            {
                "name": "Deadly",
                "url": "/topics/deadly"
            },
            {
                "name": "Rather",
                "url": "/topics/rather"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/ron_chernow_290865",
        "quote": "Because of the love affair between the American public and the stock market, it is possible for entrepreneurs, technological visionaries and inventors of every sort to get financing.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Ron Chernow",
            "url": "/quotes/ron_chernow_290865"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Love",
                "url": "/topics/love"
            },
            {
                "name": "Visionaries",
                "url": "/topics/visionaries"
            },
            {
                "name": "Inventors",
                "url": "/topics/inventors"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/ron_chernow_290866",
        "quote": "There is no country in the world where it's as easy to find venture capital in the stock market as the United States.",
